    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Medieval diner sim with roguelike elements!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a kingdom that has outlawed potion making, an herbalist turned brew-master continues to sell potions on the underground market from the back of their tavern. Serve both ale and potions to customers, but don't get caught selling potions when the guards make their rounds!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 special customers to discover and unlock, many with unique abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random world events that can change the direction of your run.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guards will be on the lookout for illegal potion sales - don't get caught!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase tavern upgrades in between days</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your tavern to accommodate more customers and serve new menu items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn gold by serving drinks to customers!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/7b98d3702c40a729de442acc6d2e5a2f.poster.avif?t=1761149557\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/7b98d3702c40a729de442acc6d2e5a2f.webm?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/7b98d3702c40a729de442acc6d2e5a2f.mp4?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Throw Tankards at bad guys to protect your loot!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/3ed5793c87842c27b0fef1e0d7d79fd3.poster.avif?t=1761149557\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/3ed5793c87842c27b0fef1e0d7d79fd3.webm?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/3ed5793c87842c27b0fef1e0d7d79fd3.mp4?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Brew potions in the back storeroom by playing a timing-based minigame.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/dd0379eccc9520dc91fca429a6fdc43e.poster.avif?t=1761149557\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/dd0379eccc9520dc91fca429a6fdc43e.webm?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243410/extras/dd0379eccc9520dc91fca429a6fdc43e.mp4?t=1761149557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
